data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom 2.5 bath home with an inground pool in established Quail Run Estates. Huge living room with fireplace and built in book shelves. This home also features an office/second living and a formal dining room. Huge screened in back patio, fully fenced back yard. Great proximity to major highways and easy access to shopping and dining at Broken Arrow hills!
